info.name: Ocean.io API Documentation
info.description:
Welcome to Ocean.io's API.
            The API can be used to access all our API endpoints, such as our enrich API to look up company information, or our discover API to identify companies based on specific search criteria such as semantic similarity, technologies or industries.
            Ocean.io's APIs are a set of HTTPS endpoints that you can use to retrieve and integrate Ocean.io's data into your existing workflows.
            All requests should be made through https and the request and response bodies should be formatted in JSON.
